#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.logical_not.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.logical\\_not"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_not.logical_not:1 of
msgid "Compute the truth value of NOT x element-wise."
msgstr "逐元素计算 NOT x 的真值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_not.logical_not of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_not.logical_not:3 of
msgid "Logical NOT is applied to the elements of `x`."
msgstr "对 `x` 的元素应用逻辑非运算。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_not.logical_not:5 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须可以广播到输入的形状。如果未提供"
"或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（只能作为关键字参数）的长度必须"
"等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_not.logical_not:10 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "为 True 的值表示在该位置计算 ufunc，为 False 的值表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_not.logical_not of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_not.logical_not:15 of
msgid ""
"**y** -- Boolean result with the same shape as `x` of the NOT operation "
"on elements of `x`."
msgstr ""
"**y** -- 与 `x` 具有相同形状的布尔结果，表示对 `x` 元素进行 NOT 运算的"
"结果。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_not.logical_not of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_not.logical_not:19 of
msgid ":py:obj:`logical_and`, :py:obj:`logical_or`, :py:obj:`logical_xor`"
msgstr ""

